        <a href="http://www.gnu.org/licenses/gpl.html">GNU General Public License</a>. 
        The source code for the Juturna project is available at
        <a href="http://git.juturna.ca/">http://git.juturna.ca</a>. (To download 
        the entire directory of source code subdirectories and files, use the command 
        "git clone gitosis@git.juturna.ca:/srv/gitosis/repositories/juturna " and the 
